            <div class="col mr-sm-2 justify-content-center">
                <h1 class="display-3 font-weight-light">About Us</h1>
                <p>
                    The "Student Council" or "Student Parliament" is a student leadership 
                    group that exists in every institution. These councils serve as a 
                    conduit between students and the college administration in order to 
                    enhance student life. Throughout the year, student councils plan and 
                    organize a variety of activities and events. Student Council 
                    representatives gather in all faculties to elect the Student Council 
                    at the community level, which represents students from all faculties 
                    locally and globally.
                </p>
            </div>
